message.help:
```yml
!help/!h: Show this message

!pack: Redirect you to the ressource-pack channel

!stats/!stat/!s [player]: Show player Hole in the Wall stats

!ping: Show how much Wally is dying

!compare/!c [player1] [player2]: Compare two player Hole in the Wall stats

!setbackground/!setbg (file required): Change you stats background

!resetbackground/!rbg: Reset your stats background

!leaderboard/!lead/!lb [W/R/Q/F/T] [page] ["discord"]: Show Hole in the Wall leaderboard

!profile/!p [player]: Show player Hypixel level and Achievement points

!changelog: Show latest Wally modification

!convert [Q/F] [score]: Convert a final score to a qualification score and the other way around
```

message.help admin:
```yml
!help/!h: Show this message

!pack: Redirect you to the ressource-pack channel

!stats/!stat/!s [player]: Show player Hole in the Wall stats

!ping: Show how much Wally is dying

!compare/!c [player1] [player2]: Compare two player Hole in the Wall stats

!setbackground/!setbg (file required): Change you stats background

!resetbackground/!rbg: Reset your stats background

!leaderboard/!lead/!lb [W/R/Q/F/T] [page] ["discord"]: Show Hole in the Wall leaderboard

!profile/!p [player]: Show player Hypixel level and Achievement points

!changelog: Show latest Wally modification

!convert [Q/F] [score]: Convert a final score to a qualification score and the other way around

!setconfig (file required): Update Wally configuration file
```
